{"tid":389534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一蚊一斤鯨】瀕危鯨鯊當街遭血腥分屍賤賣 皆因酒店嫌「太臭」？","createTime":"2017-09-06T10:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T14:33:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae002d941da70416aff3b9422c89de2c6f769874","tid":389534,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504624369_8155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504624369_8155.jpg&h=55c5031c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504624807_9b46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504624807_9b46.jpg&h=834c13cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無知？還是明知故犯？！前日，內地有網民在微博上發佈圖片，顯示一輛貨車正在運送捕撈上岸、被列為國家二級保護動物鯨鯊經過鬧市，並將其運至福州霞浦縣三沙鎮宏發大酒店，但酒店以魚太臭、不能食用為由拒收。至昨日，網絡流傳多段視頻顯示，該鯨鯊已遭切割售賣，現場十分殘忍，當地政府表示警方已經介入調查，會嚴懲涉事者。<br />\n<br />\n4日下午5時，網友@BlueGood在微博上發佈四張圖片，顯示有捕撈上岸的鯨鯊被人用貨車運載「招搖過市」。據悉，該鯨鯊曾被運至霞浦縣三沙鎮宏發大酒店，該酒店工作人員昨日坦誠，由於其位居海邊，運輸鯨鯊的人的確來過酒店，詢問是否願意收購，但酒店以「太臭了」為由拒收，讓其運走。此外，該酒店的廚師長解釋道，這種鯊魚由於在海裏生長時間過長，水銀含量很高，是不能吃的。<br />\n<br />\n昨日上午，微博陸續流傳出多段視頻。其中，一則視頻顯示有人開小貨車將鯨鯊運至某酒店旁，一則視頻顯示有兩人正在對鯨鯊的尾鰭部分進行切割，此外，兩人用鋸子來回拉扯切割鯨鯊出售。事件引起當局關注，警方已經介入調查，與此同時市海洋與漁業局也表示，將加強有關宣傳工作。<br />\n<br />\n至於這條鯨鯊是何時捕撈上岸？如何落網？漁民是否知其屬國家二級保護動物，文中並沒有交待。去年，在廣西北海水域，一條國家二級保護動物鯨鯊被捕殺，七名疑犯被捕。據捕獲鯨鯊的船長供稱，收起魚網時，鯨鯊已經死亡並發臭，加上不知道牠是國家二級保護動物，<span style=\"color: red;\">最後以每斤一元人民幣的價格轉售製造魚肥。</span><br />\n<br />\n鯨鯊屬於《瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約》附錄II物種，已被國際自然保護聯盟瀕危物種紅色名錄列為瀕危物種。根據內地最高人民法院司法解釋和《刑法》的相關規定，捕撈、出售鯨鯊的行為均觸犯刑法，將被處5年以下監禁或拘役，並處罰金。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504624803_c473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504624803_c473.jpg&h=1c833857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504624806_9113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504624806_9113.jpg&h=0e8ebc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170906/57173230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170906%2F57173230&d=eN%2Foexm6BYkdW6HtB%2B3Tn9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=20970c99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170906%2F57173230&h=d35d4b7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170906/57173230</a>"},{"pid":"2fdb88a16a561a6022009e4456546c767a5d1161","tid":389534,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"一蚊一斤鯊先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13ec2211caa2314a861f953609ec6d68f092cdb","tid":389534,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:31:32.000Z","msg":"成條都係水銀，重金屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a963c6b06c606ade2bce33af7965b298fa9bbfb","tid":389534,"uid":105410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"負皮係比視頻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4421c527cedccd6f2001476c77726a0cc4ffa928","tid":389534,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"殺鯨魚 連登仔就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3818f564b09900db4180a19f8b058932b9de0c2d","tid":389534,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"睇圖都覺得臭"},{"pid":"ce17e6d8de26bee6af5525fef6e690e792605caa","tid":389534,"uid":52819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"仲扮野撈上黎已經死左 屌你老母無文化既大陸西"},{"pid":"7fd1d2233fe54a206d18c9bafc2f7429ef3cd0d9","tid":389534,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺鯨魚 連登仔就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鯨鯊屬於鯊魚既一種唔係鯨，係世上最大既魚類！"},{"pid":"4f3fadd08d0d46c02f81a82e594760342003df50","tid":389534,"uid":81995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"拉晒去打靶就岩，鯨鯊 rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df31d0fe2158fd698a495081c58d299126cceae3","tid":389534,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇圖都覺得臭</blockquote><br />\n海洋生物係特別臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e776e3d31b052442f78470187b728b9478d70a9d","tid":389534,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成條都係水銀，重金屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那人表示唔明你講乜"}]}